h3. Problem Definition
In JIRA iOS app, there's not currently a way to create a sub-task. You can attempt to select the sub-task option, but then it gives you an error:
{quote}Issue type is a sub-task but parent issue key or id not specified{quote}
There's no field to specify the parent issue. Additionally, you cannot go to the parent task and then click to create a sub-task from there

h3. Suggested Solution
- Allow to select a parent task when creating a sub-task
- Or go to a parent task and create a sub-task from that page.

